Package poker.handCategories

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Flush
    Represents a flush, the fourth strongest hand category.
    FullHouse
    Represents a full house, the third strongest hand category.
    HandCategory
    HandCategory is the abstract base class for the different hand types you can have at showdown.
    HighCard
    Represents high card, the weakest hand category.
    OnePair
    Represents one pair, the eighth strongest hand category.
    Quads
    Represents four of a kind, the second strongest hand category.
    Straight
    Represents a straight, the fifth strongest hand category.
    StraightFlush
    Represents a straight flush, the strongest hand category.
    Trips
    Represents three of a kind, the sixth strongest hand category.
    TwoPair
    Represents two pair, the seventh strongest hand category.
